text: Krasnoarmeyskaya () is a rural locality (a village) in Pervomaysky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 241 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 60 km from Sterlitamak, 10 km from Pervomayskoye. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Krasnoarmeyskaya
